{# Region Culture Section - Cultural heritage, traditions, cuisine #}

<div class="content">
  <h3 class="title is-4">Culture & Heritage</h3>
  
  {%- if region.culture -%}
  <p>{{ region.culture.description }}</p>
  {%- else -%}
  <p>{{ region.name }} is known for its rich cultural heritage and distinct traditions passed down through generations.</p>
  {%- endif -%}

  <h4 class="title is-5 mt-5">Traditions & Customs</h4>
  <div class="box has-background-light">
    <p class="mb-3">
      The people of {{ region.name }} have maintained strong cultural traditions that reflect the region's history 
      and values. Local festivals, celebrations, and customs provide insight into the authentic character of the region.
    </p>
    {%- if region.culture and region.culture.traditions -%}
    <ul>
      {%- for tradition in region.culture.traditions -%}
      <li>{{ tradition }}</li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <h4 class="title is-5 mt-5">Cuisine & Gastronomy</h4>
  <div class="columns">
    <div class="column">
      <p class="mb-3">
        {{ region.name }}'s culinary tradition is a reflection of its geography, history, and agricultural heritage. 
        Local dishes feature fresh, seasonal ingredients and time-honored preparation methods.
      </p>
      {%- if region.culture and region.culture.specialties -%}
      <p class="heading is-size-7">Regional Specialties:</p>
      <ul class="is-size-7">
        {%- for specialty in region.culture.specialties -%}
        <li>{{ specialty }}</li>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ul>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
    <div class="column">
      {%- if region.culture and region.culture.wines -%}
      <div class="box has-background-success-light">
        <p class="heading has-text-success">Wines</p>
        <ul class="is-size-7">
          {%- for wine in region.culture.wines -%}
          <li>{{ wine }}</li>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </div>

  <h4 class="title is-5 mt-5">Arts & Heritage Sites</h4>
  <p class="mb-3">{{ region.name }} is home to numerous cultural and historical sites of significance:</p>
  <div class="columns is-multiline">
    {%- if region.culture and region.culture.sites -%}
      {%- for site in region.culture.sites -%}
      <div class="column is-full-mobile is-half-tablet is-one-third-desktop">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="title is-6">{{ site.name }}</p>
            <p class="is-size-7">{{ site.description }}</p>
            {%- if site.type -%}
            <p class="mt-2"><span class="tag is-small">{{ site.type }}</span></p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="column is-full-mobile">
        <div class="notification is-info">
          <p class="is-size-7">{{ region.name }} features several UNESCO World Heritage sites, museums, and historical landmarks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <h4 class="title is-5 mt-5">Festivals & Events</h4>
  <p class="mb-3">The region celebrates its heritage through various cultural events and festivals throughout the year:</p>
  <div class="box has-background-warning-light">
    <p class="is-size-7">
      Major festivals showcase traditional music, dance, crafts, and cuisine. These events bring together locals 
      and visitors to celebrate {{ region.name }}'s unique identity and cultural pride.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
